<span
class="card-byline-date">Jul 23, 2024</span><div
class="card-byline-bio">
Carla is a Copywriter for Zarla based in Cape Town, South Africa. She has over 5 years&#039; experience in online content creation and writes extensively on logos for small businesses.</div></div></div></div><div
