class="block-intro-text"><p>An affiliate website typically promotes other companies' products or services for commission. The affiliate marketing industry is booming and serves as a great source of income for creators, influencers, and entrepreneurs in various sectors, such as health and beauty, technology, and finance.</p><p>A memorable affiliate website should consist of pages with clear visual hierarchies and product categorizations that allow visitors to easily explore the site. Other elements that will enhance the user experience include prominent CTA buttons and a search bar. Use our review as a guide when creating your own site with our <a
href="/">affiliate AI website builder</a>.</p></div><div
